# Matrix demo — single source of truth

- **ZAX entry (default app):** `src/matrix.zax` — the RGB 8×8 matrix program. Use this path when editing, assembling, or debugging the matrix demo unless the user explicitly names another file.
- **Asm80 reference (same algorithm):** `src/matrix-demo.asm`
- **Debug80:** `.vscode/debug80.json` uses `defaultTarget` `matrix` with `asm` / `sourceFile` both `src/matrix.zax`; build artifacts are `build/matrix.*`.

Do not substitute `serial`, `examples/`, or other repos when the user means this matrix program.
